Grease 12 muffin cups. In each cup, place 2 teaspoons butter, 2 teaspoons brown sugar, three pecan halves and a dash of cinnamon. In a bowl, combine biscuit mix, applesauce and milk just until moistened. Spoon into muffin cups. Bake at 450 degrees for 10 minutes. Immediately invert onto a serving platter. Serve warm.